title: GDVS Ready to Assist Newly Eligible Agent Orange Veterans (Georgia Department of Veterans Services)
text: ( Source : Georgia Department of Veterans Services) Last week the federal Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) published a new regulation expanding eligibility to certain veterans who may have been exposed to the Vietnam-era chemical herbicide
